{
  "_meta": {
    "version": "5.0.0",
    "created": "2026-04-07",
    "description": "Advanced RL Quant Model v5 — PPO + Fama-French 5F + News-Calibrated Price Impact",
    "references": [
      "Fama, E.F. & French, K.R. (1993, 2015) — 5-factor asset pricing model",
      "Colby, R. — Post-Earnings Announcement Drift (PEAD), 20.3% annualized",
      "Bryant, L. — VADER sentiment augmented Fama-French model",
      "UCSD Research — Earnings beat price jump frequency (90%+ cases)",
      "IntechOpen — Analyst upgrades NASDAQ avg CAR: +3.17%; downgrades: -3.47%",
      "Schulman et al. (2017, arxiv:1707.06347) — Proximal Policy Optimization"
